        <definition>int conn_mgr_conn_binding::idle_timeout</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>idle_timeout</name>
        <qualifiedname>conn_mgr_conn_binding::idle_timeout</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Usage timeout (seconds) </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Indicates to the connectivity implementation how long the interface can be idle for before automatically taking the interface down.</para>
<para>Set to <ref refid="group__conn__mgr__connectivity_1ga605eee24f4419b5cd6a50a0272979da7" kindref="member">CONN_MGR_IF_NO_TIMEOUT</ref> to indicate that no idle timeout should be used. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
